The paper discusses learning to learn, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The focus is on optimization, which is a key component of many machine learning algorithms. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also uses a novel hierarchical RNN architecture and applies it to image classification tasks, which suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
